---
title: Pork Schnitzel & Zingy Apple-Bacon Slaw Panini with Potato Wedges & Garlic Aioli
description: This pork schnitzel sando is our crunchiest creation yet. Golden crumbed schnitzel and a crisp, refreshing apple and bacon slaw come together in the middle of a perfectly toasted panini for the ultimate handheld meal. That first crunch will be heard throughout the house!
